## Key Files

{{#if isMulti}}
**Sites:**
- `sites/*/vite.config.js` - Config using `defineSiteConfig()` from `@uniweb/build/site`
- `sites/*/main.js` - Entry using `start()` from `@uniweb/runtime`
- `sites/*/site.yml` - Site configuration (foundation, title, i18n)
- `sites/*/pages/` - Content pages (file-based routing)

**Foundations:**
- `foundations/*/vite.config.js` - Config using `defineFoundationConfig()` from `@uniweb/build`
- `foundations/*/src/styles.css` - Tailwind CSS v4 theme
- `foundations/*/src/components/*/meta.js` - Component metadata
- `foundations/*/src/runtime.js` - (optional) Custom Layout
{{else}}
**Site:**
- `site/vite.config.js` - Config using `defineSiteConfig()` from `@uniweb/build/site`
- `site/main.js` - Entry using `start()` from `@uniweb/runtime`
- `site/site.yml` - Site configuration (foundation, title, i18n)
- `site/pages/` - Content pages (file-based routing)

**Foundation:**
- `foundation/vite.config.js` - Config using `defineFoundationConfig()` from `@uniweb/build`
- `foundation/src/styles.css` - Tailwind CSS v4 theme
- `foundation/src/components/*/meta.js` - Component metadata
- `foundation/src/runtime.js` - (optional) Custom Layout
- `foundation/src/_entry.generated.js` - Auto-generated at build/dev
{{/if}}
